_:genid20 <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#select> "\n            PREFIX fairAss: <http://example.org/fair-assessment#>\n\n            SELECT $this\n            WHERE {\n                $this fairAss:testResult fairAss:Fail ;\n                      fairAss:value ?value .\n                FILTER (?value != 0.0)\n            }\n        " .
_:genid20 <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> "If testResult is Fail, the value must be exactly 0.0." .
_:genid20 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#SPARQLConstraint> .
<http://example.org/fair-assessment-shapes#FailResultShape> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#targetClass> <http://example.org/fair-assessment#SubPrincipleResult> .
# 
# http://example.org/fair-assessment-shapes#IndeterminateResultShape
<http://example.org/fair-assessment-shapes#IndeterminateResultShape> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<http://example.org/fair-assessment-shapes#IndeterminateResultShape> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#NodeShape> .
<http://example.org/fair-assessment-shapes#IndeterminateResultShape> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#sparql> _:genid21 .
_:genid21 <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#select> "\n            PREFIX fairAss: <http://example.org/fair-assessment#>\n\n            SELECT $this\n            WHERE {\n                $this fairAss:testResult fairAss:Indeterminate ;\n                      fairAss:value ?value .\n                FILTER (?value <= 0.0 || ?value >= 1.0)\n            }\n        " .
_:genid21 <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#message> "If testResult is Indeterminate, the value must be greater than 0 and less than 1." .
_:genid21 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#SPARQLConstraint> .
<http://example.org/fair-assessment-shapes#IndeterminateResultShape> <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#targetClass> <http://example.org/fair-assessment#SubPrincipleResult> .
